<h4 id="1--tex-and-latex">1  Tex and Latex</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Tex is about formatting</li>
  <li>Latex is about content</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="ÊúÄÁÆÄÂçïÁöÑtex‰ª£Á†Å">ÊúÄÁÆÄÂçïÁöÑTex‰ª£Á†Å</h3>
<div class="language-latex highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">\documentclass</span><span class="na">[11pt]</span><span class="p">{</span>article<span class="p">}</span>
<span class="nt">\begin{document}</span>
<span class="nt">\end{document}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>there are two ways to get a line break
type two backslashes
a blank line</p>

